{"tid":1378363,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《十年》真係好撚好睇。","createTime":"2019-07-28T15:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T18:01:13.000Z","uid":239078,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ce4db89ee3564fd11222315b38a43a2b4dabf9","tid":1378363,"uid":239078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:41:24.000Z","msg":"呢幾日發咗好多個夢，情緒有啲低落，所以呢一個鐘冇再睇任何live，放鬆一吓，諗住會好翻啲。今日睇到個post 關於前幾年嘅一套戲《十年》，所以就喺網上再翻睇多一次，然後心情再更加低落。我心入面有好多嘢想講，所以我喺套戲度cap咗啲對白想表達我嘅心情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6m2dKPg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6m2dKPg.png&h=e4d15046&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2X5AVX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2X5AVX.png&h=297caf41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWgRwui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWgRwui.png&h=7f608be0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQr92AZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQr92AZ.png&h=bc64b864&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NFTHC9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNFTHC9k.png&h=9601bfdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS如果未睇過真係要去睇吓，如果你係人，一個有良心嘅人，你一定會有感受。"},{"pid":"d2e4d5a561f60f673b7b90f1dbce8bce65bbd3b1","tid":1378363,"uid":239078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"香港人，加油。"},{"pid":"99ccd3bc95b9321edbcf43993f83934c998a811c","tid":1378363,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"唔放棄"},{"pid":"0eea2aeed3eb94a09a2992a57d957c891eac4855","tid":1378363,"uid":268868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"十年 <br />\n係一本預言書"},{"pid":"9a1d5f6917e93a055bdfa8810e99ac51c8dc94ea","tid":1378363,"uid":23256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-